n1. 係中學門口派港獨傳單, 向中學生宣傳港獨理念, 與中共的國教科對抗<br />\n<br />\n2. 去日本, 與新疆獨立代表, 西藏獨立代表, 內蒙古獨立代表 見會, 一齊商量如何脫離中共統治, 獨立"},{"pid":"56e34e7e2d21a0534f1f4287d03c4e000bcfe153","tid":106196,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:15:50.000Z","msg":"本土新聞同本土研究社啦"},{"pid":"75bafad419aeca14f02a0ccb0253ee413aed52b0","tid":106196,"uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:15:50.000Z","msg":"捐俾薯片叔叔，都嚟方會撐港獨啦，都唔同對象"},{"pid":"2ca46b139d8fddb58b0f60ec3f056a3c159ddd1b","tid":106196,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:17:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢班人殺雞都冇力，捐比佢<span style=\"color: red;\">用黎報psyhical?</span></blockquote><br />\n飲緊野忍唔住噴咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6116a8efb4d29fce23b6c008f6cfdc5da942c9a1","tid":106196,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:17:52.000Z","msg":"港語學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日既香港，大陸化嚴重，係政府推波助瀾之下，有大量中小學都開始以普通話教授中文，對以廣東話為母語既香港學生黎講，到底影響有幾深?<br />\n<br />\n唔知佢地既捐款方式係點，可以email問問阿行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nEmail: [url]hongkonglanglearn@gmail.com[/url]"},{"pid":"749b0dc545346941fd98bba38a2ed45c8f1de9e4","tid":106196,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:19:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>民族黨又搞得咩出樣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你無留意新聞就以為人地無做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n民族黨目前有以下成績<br />\n<br />\n1. 係中學門口派港獨傳單, 向中學生宣傳港獨理念, 與中共的國教科對抗<br />\n<br />\n2. 去日本, 與新疆獨立代表, 西藏獨立代表, 內蒙古獨立代表 見會, 一齊商量如何脫離中共統治, 獨立</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac4da83583cbf7c215ff25f96de47aa401e85197","tid":106196,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:21:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本土新聞同本土研究社啦</blockquote><br />\nyes 仲有本土研究社<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n捐助我們<br />\n<br />\n本土研究社開拓各種自主獨立的本土研究，推動民間知識生產與普及，請捐款支持本土研究社的工作。<br />\n捐款方法 &mdash; 直接存入中國銀行戶口：012-588-1-036873-6<br />\n<br />\n研究項目                                                                                                                                                                                       <br />\n<br />\n香港土地問題研究報告&mdash;&mdash;真相與迷思<br />\n<br />\n自去年被林鄭成功營造出一種香港需要「增加土地供應」的議程後，探求土地真相與迷思的研究工作其實已經來晚了，在鄉郊土地與融合到境等危機前必須盡快開催！<br />\n<br />\n籌款目標: $30000            現籌得: $0  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://localresearchcommunity.wordpress.com/donation/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flocalresearchcommunity.wordpress.com%2Fdonation%2F&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhpgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=5cb4f92c\" target=\"_blank\">https://localresearchcommunity.wordpress.com/donation/</a>"},{"pid":"4e507dcb6580246f4cb8dfbeeecfa477c70756ed","tid":106196,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f20aadedc43a6476ed9703117063fc72119bd8e6","tid":106196,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:57:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家鬥乞錢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18fe5222c51affa9cba10cb337a2fd75a01f012b","tid":106196,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:58:35.000Z","msg":"實後悔"},{"pid":"361d8fa2468da5bee86e1d6f9b41548a90b5a681","tid":106196,"uid":35683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T15:34:29.000Z","msg":"以上從未見過有任何可以幫助香港市民作為，點捐呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}